pos review: Location was great and staff very helpful. Airport transfer was easy and good value for money.
neg review: The level of cleaning was under all levels. "No smoking" - room? Really strong smell of tobacco!

pos review: Fitness centre, free parking, good location, very quite room

pos review: Great setting - nice view over the fabulously Soviet post office or Lenin square.

pos review: Clean hotel, friendly staff. Location is in the centre of the city.
